        "description": "Creates a **Map Layer Summary** for the field. The response typically includes a **Location** header with the new summary URI—use it in subsequent steps.\n\n**OAuth scope:** `ag3`\n\n**Request URL:** `POST https://sandboxapi.deere.com/platform/organizations/{orgId}/fields/{id}/mapLayerSummaries`",
        "security": [{ "OAuth2AuthorizationCode": ["ag3"] }],
        "parameters": [
